# Recommended Packages

## Backend

```bash
npm install express mongoose cors dotenv nodemon
```

Purpose:
- express → backend framework
- mongoose → MongoDB
- cors → frontend/backend communication
- dotenv → environment variables
- nodemon → auto restart

